---
// [11] Final CTA — Allocated gold, settled globally.
---

<section class="section cta-section" id="access" aria-labelledby="cta-heading">
  <div class="container container--narrow cta-section__inner">
    <p class="eyebrow reveal">The Global Gold Standard</p>
    <h2 class="display display--xl reveal" id="cta-heading" data-reveal-delay="0.05">
      Allocated gold, settled globally.
    </h2>
    <p class="cta-section__body reveal" data-reveal-delay="0.1">
      Gold does not need to become something else to participate in modern
      markets. It needs a standard that lets real bars, real vaults, and real
      title operate across a global liquidity network.
    </p>
    <p class="cta-section__final reveal" data-reveal-delay="0.13">
      Global Gold is building that standard.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-section__actions reveal" data-reveal-delay="0.16">
      <a class="cta--box" href="/standard/">Explore the Standard</a>
      <a class="cta" href="/docs/">Read the Documentation →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section__inner { text-align: center; }
  .cta-section h2 {
    max-width: 18ch;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-top: 0.4em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .cta-section__body {
    margin: clamp(28px, 3.6vw, 44px) auto 0;
    max-width: 56ch;
    font-size: var(--t-lede);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--graphite);
  }
  .cta-section__final {
    margin: clamp(20px, 2.4vw, 32px) auto 0;
    font-family: var(--serif-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.4vw, 2.1rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--char);
  }
  .cta-section__actions {
    margin-top: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
